caption: Good food

I meet friends in this nice place often! This is my favorite restaurant to grab a bite.  I visit this spot at least once a month. The meals are excellent, the team is welcoming and the cost is good. I enjoy meeting in this spot for a decent dinner.

Mr Bibi is our go to place in Oceanside. Bowls are delicious. Ingredients are fresh. You get to pick and choose what you want in your bowl. Their fried chicken is crispy and savory. The owners are passionate about cooking and will customize as much as possible to make you happy!!

AMAZING!! Delicious, delicious food. Ate here while visiting and was schocked to find most people I recommended it too hadn’t tried it. The food was DELICIOUS and I can’t wait to come back. The staff were friendly, the restaurant was clean and informative, the experience was everything.

I wish I took a picture...we ordered 2 of the hot bowls and order of wings.  Just awesome.  Perfection. The bowls were so good,  I had half brown rice half noodle with bolgogi and spicy pork and my choice of additions with the egg of course …
Fusion bowl is great
Very good food.
Great food, great service. The place is very clean, too.

I’m a big foodie at heart and usually don’t end up being a regular at most places because I like trying out new restaurants. But this place is really good. Best Korean food you can find in north county imo. Small mom and pop place, very friendly staff and reasonable priced food! Love the stone bowl bibimbap, it’s a must try!
What a wonderful place. Can't believe I have only just found it. Must go back soon. Both food and service unbeatable.
Very tasty! Friendly staff and fast service! Definitely gotta try
Food is awesome hot bowls are delicious 😋
Great Place to take the Family!
It was delicious, the best restaurant I've tried in Oceanside. Will be coming back for more!

Been here a few times. The experience is good. Very tasty food. The only complaint I have is today they sold out of most  food before the last hr before closing, so I only had one choice from the menu. But I guess that's a good thing they are busy during these times. Good for them.
Incredible food and lovely folks who run the place.  This is a must stop if you are in Oceanside!
Very, very salty. People were friendly.
Great place to go for Korean food! Stone bowls and vegan friendly. The staff is happy and easy to order - worth stopping for lunch or dinner. They also have beer 🍻

Our first trying Korean food. OMG!!!!!!! That was sooooo good! And the service was awesome too. They explained a about the food and the owner even came out to check on us while we were eating! We will be back...even if we have to drive 40 miles. Totally worth it!!

It was amazing korean food!. Me and my daughter loves it. The price to me is cheap compare to go to other korean restaurant. Service was amazing too. Amazing couple. Fast, clean and cheap. We definately will come back!

Authentic Korean food. Reminded me of the time I spent in Seoul. The serving size was very generous and the price very good for what you get. Various toppings to choose from. Three outdoor tables for dine in. We loved this place.
Food is delicious and affordable. The environment is very inviting.
A great Korean rice or noodle bowl place.

Great food! Expect to pay a bit more than other places of larger establishment, but the staff here are friendly and helpful and the flavors are arguably better. Their hot stone bowls are a great meal especially on a cold day. Also, if you're of age, you must try the Soju(korean wine) !
Great food...  one classic and one hot pot
Super expensive 😫
Excellent food, they have couple tables outside or you can take your food and eat it by the fountain. Overall great service!

The food here is amazing but what made this go to a 5 star was the service. Being a small restaurant they're so friendly and the music was spot on. But on to the main portion of this review. What I highly recommend is their Calamari appetizers. If you're in oceanside I highly recommend this place.
Korean fusion bowls definitely worth the extra buck to get the hot bowl.

I’m not one to normally review restaurants, but I have never been dissatisfied with the food or the service here at Mr. Bibi. The restaurant is clean, the food is great, and the service is great. If it can be put in a bowl, I’ve probably had it in mine, and I have yet to be disappointed.

Very elegant and accessible place. They offer big portions and for fair prices. We enjoyed the meals very much and the waiters were very welcoming and chatty. Recommended.
Excellent service for quick and healthy options. The bibimbap is solid but the korean chicken really shines.

The best local Korean restaurant!! As a Korean myself, it is hard for me to find a Korean place that actually tastes good, but I love this place. Quick service and amazing food.

Easily the best place to eat in town!
Food is always great!
So delicious. 😋 10/10 would recommend.

Can’t believe I’ve never tried this place. Amazing flavors, generous portions, and reasonable prices. A great addition to the diverse cuisine offered in downtown Oceanside. Staff was very friendly as well. Will definitely be recommending to local friends who have unknowingly missed out on this place.
Very generous portion,  if your hungry you may be able to finish a big bowl. Lots of goodies on top and fun flavor too. I love it, and its family owned so you know there is Love in the food.

It takes your bibimbap to the next level. I'm so happy that I found this place and come back often since the bowls never seem the same.

Came yere on a whim. The food was very delicious, abd the prices were great for the amount of food given. Hace recommended this place to multiple friends since.
